title: #92Noon Live at Training Camp! Friday Feastin' for Day 1 Walkthroughs
description:
The FAN's Paul Allen, Paul Charchian, and Eric Nordquist are live from the exclusive KFAN Radio Perch on this first day of walkthroughs.

Vikings quarterback Kirk Cousins joins the Feast, and more!
